data.description: This charming pool home is centrally located in Boynton Beach's all-ages, gated community of Crystal Key. To be able own a Single Family Home with all of the following qualities at this price point is a RARITY - 2 miles from the beach. Gated neighborhood entry for residents only. LOW HOA dues. Your own Private Pool. Attached Garage. 3-Minutes from I95. Surrounded by convenience, restaurants & shoppes.  All-Ages are welcome, but most importantly so are Pets. They will love the fenced in backyard along with the perfectly manicured sidewalks throughout the neighborhood. Only 1 other home has sold in entire the community since 2021. Why? Because owners absolutely love it here.
